title: Belichick returns to coaching, this time at UNC
description: Six-time Super Bowl-winning head coach Bill Belichick has been named the new head coach at North Carolina.

title: Sources: Rodriguez poised for W. Virginia return
description: Rich Rodriguez is set to return as coach of West Virginia, a program that has struggled since joining the Big 12 and will hope to restore the type of success he led during his time there from 2001 to '07.
author: Pete Thamel

title: 'Never seen a Guardiola team this bad' - Man City under 'real pressure'
description: With one win in 10 games in all competitions and facing a real battle to progress in the Champions League, Manchester City are described as "under real pressure"' to turn their form around.

title: 'Scary how good he will be' - 'special' Saka inspires Arsenal
description: Bukayo Saka is enjoying a superb season with Arsenal and proves his worth again with an inspirational display in their Champions League win over Monaco.

title: For North Carolina, the risk of hiring Bill Belichick is worth it
description: Plenty of NFL coaches have gone to the college ranks and failed. But this is a new era in college sports, and Belichick with his 8 Super Bowl rings could deliver big.
author: Yahoo Sports

title: Reports: West Virginia finalizing deal with Rich Rodriguez
description: Rodriguez was WVU's coach from 2001 through 2007.
author: Yahoo Sports

title: Saudi Arabia awarded 2034 World Cup as 2030 hosts also confirmed
description: FIFA has confirmed the 2034 World Cup will be held in Saudi Arabia, while the 2030 World Cup will be co-hosted by Spain, Portugal and Morocco with the opening three matches in South America.

title: Rashford among Man Utd stars available for transfer
description: Marcus Rashford is one of several Manchester United players available for transfer as INEOS try to raise funds to reinvest in the squad.
